<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TIM11">
<l>kaḻaṟkoṇṭa cēvaṭi kāṇaluṟ ṟārtammaip pēṇaluṟṟār</l>
<l>niḻaṟkaṇṭa pōḻtattu nillā viṉainika retumiṉṟit</l>
<l>taḻaṟkoṇṭa cōtic cemmēṉiyem māṉaikkaim māmalartūyt</l>
<l>toḻakkaṇṭu niṟkiṟku mōtuṉṉi nammaṭun tolviṉaiyē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Karma does not stay at the time of seeing the shadow of those who have undertaken</l>
<l>to see [his] ankleted red feet, of those who have undertaken to honour him.</l>
<l>Will our murderous old karma approach [and] stay when seeing [us] worship,</l>
<l>strewing with [your] hands big blossoms for our lord with a red body with a firery lustre that does not have its like?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
